                    <h2>About Us</h2>
					<p>Dr. Schulze’s American Botanical Pharmacy is a growth-oriented and purpose-driven distributor of quality herbal products. Our people love challenges, take ownership and thrive in a fast-paced environment. Most important, we are passionate about creating powerful health for all and a culture of service excellence, internally and externally. If you find our philosophy to be a perfect match, please apply for our Senior Recruiter position with competitive compensation. This position will be based in our beautiful headquarters in Marina Del Rey.</p>
                    <h2>EXECUTIVE SUMMARY</h2>
                    <p>We are currently seeking a Contract Recruiter to help fulfill staffing needs as the organization grows. This position is highly visible and current contract will extend at least into 2015. This recruiter will be responsible for managing clients and candidates throughout the full recruiting cycle: sourcing, screening, and managing employer brand in the talent marketplace. The primary focus is to fill officer-level exempt roles as well non-exempt roles by prioritizing workload in a fast-paced business environment. This role reports to the Director of Human Resources and is ideal for a proven talent scout who is passionate about helping organizations win through talent acquisition.</p>
